msContents.summary: Correspondence of several generations of the Acciaiuoli family of Florence, concerning church and secular politics as well as family affairs. Numerous letters show their strong relationship with the Papal States and with the Medici family, as well as with some other powerful aristocrats in Florence, Naples, and Ascoli.
msContents.textLang: In Italian, with some letters to Donato Acciaiuoli in Latin
